  "detailed_description": "<h1>Don't Push Your Luck</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this atmospheric <strong>card</strong> game : </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play rounds of deadly <strong>Blackjack ! </strong>try to get as close to <strong>21</strong> with your cards to win a round ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you win a round you survive till the next one. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However if you lose it... You must try your luck with a loaded <strong>revolver</strong> in a true <strong>Russian Roulette</strong> style !!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615940/extras/d9f7476166bd6b428b4c9e41ed9036c2.poster.avif?t=1771421445\" width=654 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615940/extras/d9f7476166bd6b428b4c9e41ed9036c2.webm?t=1771421445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615940/extras/d9f7476166bd6b428b4c9e41ed9036c2.mp4?t=1771421445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>Kill or be Killed</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you play your cards right, you <strong>might</strong> live to see a new day...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615940/extras/48116117c4c0684d995e1002ac09b8f8.poster.avif?t=1771421445\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615940/extras/48116117c4c0684d995e1002ac09b8f8.webm?t=1771421445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3615940/extras/48116117c4c0684d995e1002ac09b8f8.mp4?t=1771421445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short Blackjack game with a twist !</p>",
